# MAC-Specific Tasks
*Woof! Here are the special tasks for our Mac friends!*

## Environment Setup
- [ ] Check Python version (3.8+ required)
- [ ] Verify homebrew installation
- [ ] Set up virtual environment
- [ ] Install required packages

## Daily Tasks
- [ ] Check system updates
- [ ] Verify backup status
- [ ] Monitor disk space

## Development Tasks
- [ ] Test Mac-specific UI elements
- [ ] Verify file paths (Mac uses forward slashes)
- [ ] Check file permissions

